OrzHTTPd - Orz HTTP Server

    Author: Bor-Yeh Shen <byshen@cs.nctu.edu.tw>

===============================================================================

Server features:

    - Partial HTTP/1.1 support (GET, HEAD)
    - Event-driven
    - Keep-alive connections
    - Digest (MD5) authorization
    - Directory indexes 
    - User home directories
    - Virtual hosts
    - MIME settings
    - Logging
    - IPv6 support
    - Custom error messages
    - XML-based configuration file

